- "Summary of power consumption" refers to the calculated values of average power and total energy in kWh; 
- "Total energy in kWh" is calculated by summing the power consumption values and dividing by 1000 to convert watts to kilowatts, then considering the time duration in hours; 
- "Month of January 2023" specifies the time period between January 1, 2023, and January 31, 2023.
